        "desc": "<p>斯庫拉是龍蜥之王，同時也是雷穆斯的摯友。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/07/142453215/762d24fb00dcfe355802e7181da1a743_1003267582053092734.png",
