        "desc": "<p>建立雷穆利亞之王。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/24/142453215/54fc33ab94abb4b00460e448f7765892_8439986724498582331.png",
