        "name": "卡西奧多",
        "desc": "<p>「黃金獵人」，雷穆斯身邊的調律師之一。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/23/142453215/1df790c1e63e81f4bb2f0d7d429c0954_3393102207854416816.png",
        "displayStyle": "card",
